flowchart TB
    P([Proposed use]) --> REG[Purpose registration]
    REG --> TRIAGE{{Use classification<br/>Class 0-4}}
    TRIAGE -->|Class 0-1| L[Lightweight review]
    TRIAGE -->|Class 2-3| S[Standard review]
    TRIAGE -->|Class 4| F[Full governance board]
    L --> DEC{Approve?}
    S --> DEC
    F --> DEC
    DEC -->|No| REJECT[[Rejected with reasons]]
    DEC -->|Yes| REG2[Registered use]
    REG2 --> MON[/Purpose-bound access<br/>and audit logging/]
    MON --> PER[Periodic review]
    PER -->|Continue| MON
    PER -->|Modify| REG
    PER -->|Retire| RET([Use retired])
    MON -.->|Misuse or drift| INC[Governance incident]
    INC --> ROLL[[Rollback and appeal]]
    ROLL --> PER
